script = ExtResource("2_t1y56")
original_script = "IF benedictMole == 0 | GOTO | BENE_0
IF benedictMole == 1 | GOTO | BENE_1
IF benedictMole == 2 | GOTO | BENE_2
IF benedictMole == 3 | GOTO | BENE_3

BENE_3
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Come on man, you gotta help me! Give me some juicy intel or something.
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Umm... no.

BENE_2
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Come on, man! Scram! We gotta keep our distance or the duergs will get suspicious!

BENE_1
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Pfft! Get the heck out of my face, loser!

BENE_0
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Hey, what's up? I'm P_NAME_S. I'm new.
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | New? You wouldn't happen to be affiliated with L.O.N.G.I.N.U.S., now would you?
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Why do you want to know?
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Look, just cut the crud, okay? I'm all business, no pleasure.
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Who exactly are you?
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | I'm the secret informant working for L.O.N.G.I.N.U.S. from within the system.
CHOICE | Secret informant?!
IF operationX == 5  | REPLY  | INTEL_GIVE | Hey, I think I have some intel for you.
REPLY  | INTEL_DONT | I'm not convinced.
REPLY  | INTEL_NARY | Nary ye mind...

INTEL_GIVE
DIALOG | P_NAME | Hey, I think I have some intel for you. Take a look at this.
NOTE   | select | Benedict Mole-Judas
IF note == exit | GOTO | NOTE_EXIT
IF note == none | GOTO | NOTE_NONE
IF note == Sealed Secret Dossier | GOTO | NOTE_DOSSIER
IF note == Resealed Secret Dossier | GOTO | NOTE_DOSSIER
IF note == Re-resealed Secret Dossier | GOTO | NOTE_DOSSIER
IF note == Re-re-resealed Secret Dossier | GOTO | NOTE_DOSSIER
IF note == Resealed Dossier | GOTO | NOTE_DOSSIER
GOTO   | NOTE_OTHER

NOTE_OTHER
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | What? This is a total piece of shit! Why would you try to give me this?
DIALOG | P_NAME              | I thought that-
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | You thought wrong! Get a clue, newbie! You're not worth my breath. Get the heck out of my face!
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Sheesh...
QUEST  | benedictMole = 1

NOTE_EXIT
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Actually, nary ye mind...
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | What? Are you just trying to goof on me? You son of a scrooge!
DIALOG | P_NAME              | No, I'm not goofing on you, I'm just-
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Shut it! Shut your trap, newbie! You're not worth my breath. Get the heck out of my face!
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Sheesh...
QUEST  | benedictMole = 1

NOTE_NONE
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Well?
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Sorry, I got nothing.
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Pfft! Go flip yourself, newbie! You're not worth my breath. Get the heck out of my face!
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Sheesh...
QUEST  | benedictMole = 1

NOTE_DOSSIER
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Wow! This looks like something super important.
NOTE   | give | Sealed Secret Dossier
NOTE   | give | Resealed Secret Dossier
NOTE   | give | Re-resealed Secret Dossier
NOTE   | give | Re-re-resealed Secret Dossier
WAIT   | 1
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Aren't you going to open it?
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | What are you bonkers? This is my ticket out of this craphole.
DIALOG | P_NAME = s_port_hoopzSurprise | What? What do you mean?
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Uh, nothing. Forget I said anything. It's uh... top secret. Just act like none of this ever happened.
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Umm... Okay.
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | Now get the flip out of here. We have to keep our distance so the duergs don't get suspicious.
QUEST  | benedictMole = 2

INTEL_DONT
DIALOG | P_NAME              | I'm not too convinced about you being L.O.N.G.I.N.U.S..
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | What? Hey man, do you see this green armband? That's all the proof you need. Come on man, you gotta help me! Give me some juicy intel or something.
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Maybe some other time.
QUEST  | benedictMole = 3

INTEL_NARY
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Nary ye mind...
DIALOG | Benedict Mole-Judas | What? Hey man, don't leave me hanging. Come on man, you gotta help me! Give me some juicy intel or something.
DIALOG | P_NAME              | Maybe some other time.
QUEST  | benedictMole = 3"
